scopecontent.p:
The collection spans the years 1894-1957 and includes newspaper and magazine print
                advertisements for companies which were competitors of JWT clients. Product
                categories include automobiles and transportation; bakeries and baked goods;
                beverages including alcoholic, carbonated, bottled water, coffee and soft drinks;
                cleaning products; cosmetics, shaving preparations and other toiletries; dairy
                products; food including pet foods; gasoline, oil and other petroleum products;
                newspapers and magazines; over-the-counter pharmaceuticals; and tobacco products
                including cigars, cigarettes and pipe tobacco.
